														</div>
			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-2467964">
									

<p>The implication is that the artist has spent several years or decades learning about the Foundation, to the point that he's aware of the identities of specific Foundation individuals, knows how their task forces are organized, and knows the designations and compositions of several Keter-class anomalies.</p>
<p>Chances are he's made contacts with someone on the inside aside from the late Zoe, who is capable of passing mnestics to him (along with, you know, blood plasma from a reality-bending lucid dreamer).</p>
<p>Alternatively, it's possible he learned how to manufacture them himself based on information he got from his sources in the Foundation.</p>

							</div>

								
