<p>I find the AWCY? format difficult to use, as it needs to tell a story while describing potential art in practical terms. It's a story about a technical description of a piece of visual art, which feels like three things that are mutually antagonistic. I personally have had an AWCY? concept for awhile and it isn't working.</p>
<p>This works, and uses one of the more hauntingly weird SCPs to do it. I am impressed.</p>

